<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the Album Register application.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect information you provide directly to us when managing your album collection, including album titles, artists, release dates, and genre preferences.</p>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>The information we collect is used solely to provide and improve the Album Register service, including displaying your album collection and enabling search and filtering features.</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Your album data is stored locally on your device.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us.</p>
